    <div class="sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[400px] w-[250px] h-[300px] mt-[2rem] z-10">
      <img
        src="/Lady.png"
        alt="Lady"
        class="sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[400px] w-[250px] h-[300px]"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="sm:hidden mb-[11rem] sm:mb-0">
      <div
        class="h-[180px] w-[180px] border-2 border-gold rounded-full absolute -right-[10%] -translate-y-[60%]"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-[120px] w-[120px] border-[1px] border-green rounded-full absolute translate-y-[20%] translate-x-[90%]"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="w-[150px] h-[150px] absolute left-[2%] sm:hidden translate-y-[20%]"
      >
        <img src="/Tomatoes.png" alt="tomatoes" class="w-[150px] h-[150px]" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="sm:flex sm:items-start sm:mt-[4rem] sm:pl-5 md:gap-[5rem] lg:gap-[10rem]"
  >
    <div class="w-[300px] h-[340px] hidden sm:block">
      <img src="/about.png" alt="Lady" class="w-[300px] h-[300px]" />
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-9 sm:mt-0 sm:max-w-[300px] md:max-w-[350px]"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center text-green font-black gap-0"
        id="about"
      >
        <h3 class="text-[25px]">About</h3>
        <span class="text-[36px]">Shamba Data</span>
      </div>
      <article class="text-center text-xl sm:text-lg font-light mx-1">
        We understand that you struggle to get the market
        information you want.
      </article>
      <article
        class="text-center text-xl sm:text-lg font-light mt-2 sm:mt-0 mx-2"
      >
        Therefore, <span class="text-green">farmer</span>  come join <span class="text-gold">Shamba data.</span> 
        We provide you with accurate and up-to-date market information that helps you maximize profits from farming.
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="sm:hidden mb-[21rem] relative mt-6">
      <div
        class="h-[200px] w-[200px] border-2 border-gold rounded-full absolute -left-[20%]"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-[100px] w-[100px] border-2 border-green rounded-full absolute translate-y-[120%] translate-x-[20%]"
      >
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="w-[180px] h-[220px] absolute -right-0 z-[2]">
          <img src="/babu.png" alt="babu" class="w-[180px] h-[220px]" />
        </div>

        <div
          class="w-[200px] h-[200px] rounded-full absolute border-[0.5px] border-green -right-[20%] translate-y-[50%] z-1"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
